{{notability|date=February 2017}}{{Orphan|date=October 2016}}
'''Sky-Fraud''' is an open registration [[Russian language]] [[crime forum]] that has operated since 2014. It's user base consists of 26,000 active in Russian and English.<ref>{{cite news|last1=Francis|first1=Ryan|title=Darkweb marketplaces can get you more than just spam and phish|url=http://www.csoonline.com/article/3130137/security/darkweb-marketplaces-can-get-you-more-than-just-spam-and-phish.html#slide2|accessdate=16 October 2016|date=13 October 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Błaszczykiewicz|first1=Dominik|title=Dark Web: mroczny rynek, na którym znajdziesz wszystko. A zwłaszcza to, co nielegalne|url=http://www.pcworld.pl/news/Dark.Web.mroczny.rynek.na.ktorym.znajdziesz.wszystko.A.zwlaszcza.to.co.nielegalne,406675.html|accessdate=9 February 2017|date=5 December 2016}}</ref> Services include:
* [[Escrow]] services * [[Bulletproof hosting]] * Personal information for [[carding (fraud)|carding]] purposes * Sale of [[Botnets]], Exploits and Malware. * [[Black-hat SEO]] and Web design. * Payment Systems such as [[Bitcoin]], [[Paypal]], [[Webmoney]] and Entropay.
